    "markdown": "---\ntitle: Hypothesis Testing with Dependent-Samples *t*-tests\nsubtitle: Practice Problems for PSY 241\nauthor: Guenther, Benjamin A.\nproject:\n  type: website\n  output-dir: docs\nformat: \n  html:\n    html-math-method: mathjax\n    self-contained-math: false\n    embed-resources: false\njupyter: python3\n---\n\n\n\nGiven the following within-subjects data, is $M_D$ significantly less than ${0}$?  Use a ${1}$ tailed-test with $\\alpha = {0.05}$<br><br>\n```{=html}\n<style type=\"text/css\">\n</style>\n<table id=\"T_1b6e4\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th id=\"T_1b6e4_level0_col0\" class=\"col_heading level0 col0\" >ID</th>\n      <th id=\"T_1b6e4_level0_col1\" class=\"col_heading level0 col1\" >A</th>\n      <th id=\"T_1b6e4_level0_col2\" class=\"col_heading level0 col2\" >B</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_1b6e4_row0_col0\" class=\"data row0 col0\" >1</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1b6e4_row0_col1\" class=\"data row0 col1\" >22</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1b6e4_row0_col2\" class=\"data row0 col2\" >24</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_1b6e4_row1_col0\" class=\"data row1 col0\" >2</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1b6e4_row1_col1\" class=\"data row1 col1\" >22</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1b6e4_row1_col2\" class=\"data row1 col2\" >25</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_1b6e4_row2_col0\" class=\"data row2 col0\" >3</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1b6e4_row2_col1\" class=\"data row2 col1\" >26</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1b6e4_row2_col2\" class=\"data row2 col2\" >25</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_1b6e4_row3_col0\" class=\"data row3 col0\" >4</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1b6e4_row3_col1\" class=\"data row3 col1\" >25</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1b6e4_row3_col2\" class=\"data row3 col2\" >26</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_1b6e4_row4_col0\" class=\"data row4 col0\" >5</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1b6e4_row4_col1\" class=\"data row4 col1\" >23</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1b6e4_row4_col2\" class=\"data row4 col2\" >25</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_1b6e4_row5_col0\" class=\"data row5 col0\" >6</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1b6e4_row5_col1\" class=\"data row5 col1\" >23</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1b6e4_row5_col2\" class=\"data row5 col2\" >25</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_1b6e4_row6_col0\" class=\"data row6 col0\" >7</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1b6e4_row6_col1\" class=\"data row6 col1\" >26</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1b6e4_row6_col2\" class=\"data row6 col2\" >25</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_1b6e4_row7_col0\" class=\"data row7 col0\" >8</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1b6e4_row7_col1\" class=\"data row7 col1\" >23</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1b6e4_row7_col2\" class=\"data row7 col2\" >27</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_1b6e4_row8_col0\" class=\"data row8 col0\" >9</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1b6e4_row8_col1\" class=\"data row8 col1\" >24</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1b6e4_row8_col2\" class=\"data row8 col2\" >29</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n```\n<br>Summary statistics for these data:<br>\n                             $$M_A = {23.78}, M_B = {25.67}$$\n                             $$n = {9}$$ <br>\n                             \nState the Hypotheses <br>\n                            $$H_0: \\mu_D \\geq 0$$\n                            $$H_1: \\mu_D \\lt 0$$ <br>\n                            \n<br>The decision criteria: <br><br>\n$t_{crit} = {-1.86}, \\alpha_{one-tailed} = {0.05}, df = {8}$<br><br>\nCalculating the difference scores $D = X_B - X_A$ <br>\n```{=html}\n<style type=\"text/css\">\n</style>\n<table id=\"T_1474d\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th id=\"T_1474d_level0_col0\" class=\"col_heading level0 col0\" >ID</th>\n      <th id=\"T_1474d_level0_col1\" class=\"col_heading level0 col1\" >A</th>\n      <th id=\"T_1474d_level0_col2\" class=\"col_heading level0 col2\" >B</th>\n      <th id=\"T_1474d_level0_col3\" class=\"col_heading level0 col3\" >D</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_1474d_row0_col0\" class=\"data row0 col0\" >1</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1474d_row0_col1\" class=\"data row0 col1\" >22</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1474d_row0_col2\" class=\"data row0 col2\" >24</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1474d_row0_col3\" class=\"data row0 col3\" >2</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_1474d_row1_col0\" class=\"data row1 col0\" >2</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1474d_row1_col1\" class=\"data row1 col1\" >22</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1474d_row1_col2\" class=\"data row1 col2\" >25</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1474d_row1_col3\" class=\"data row1 col3\" >3</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_1474d_row2_col0\" class=\"data row2 col0\" >3</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1474d_row2_col1\" class=\"data row2 col1\" >26</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1474d_row2_col2\" class=\"data row2 col2\" >25</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1474d_row2_col3\" class=\"data row2 col3\" >-1</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_1474d_row3_col0\" class=\"data row3 col0\" >4</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1474d_row3_col1\" class=\"data row3 col1\" >25</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1474d_row3_col2\" class=\"data row3 col2\" >26</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1474d_row3_col3\" class=\"data row3 col3\" >1</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_1474d_row4_col0\" class=\"data row4 col0\" >5</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1474d_row4_col1\" class=\"data row4 col1\" >23</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1474d_row4_col2\" class=\"data row4 col2\" >25</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1474d_row4_col3\" class=\"data row4 col3\" >2</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_1474d_row5_col0\" class=\"data row5 col0\" >6</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1474d_row5_col1\" class=\"data row5 col1\" >23</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1474d_row5_col2\" class=\"data row5 col2\" >25</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1474d_row5_col3\" class=\"data row5 col3\" >2</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_1474d_row6_col0\" class=\"data row6 col0\" >7</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1474d_row6_col1\" class=\"data row6 col1\" >26</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1474d_row6_col2\" class=\"data row6 col2\" >25</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1474d_row6_col3\" class=\"data row6 col3\" >-1</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_1474d_row7_col0\" class=\"data row7 col0\" >8</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1474d_row7_col1\" class=\"data row7 col1\" >23</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1474d_row7_col2\" class=\"data row7 col2\" >27</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1474d_row7_col3\" class=\"data row7 col3\" >4</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_1474d_row8_col0\" class=\"data row8 col0\" >9</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1474d_row8_col1\" class=\"data row8 col1\" >24</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1474d_row8_col2\" class=\"data row8 col2\" >29</td>\n      <td id=\"T_1474d_row8_col3\" class=\"data row8 col3\" >5</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n```\n<br>Calculate the Mean of the Difference Scores\n                            $$M_D = \\frac{\\Sigma D}{n}$$ <br>\n                            $$M_D = \\frac{17}{9}$$ <br>\n                            $$M_D = {1.89}$$ <br><br>\n                            \nCreate a column for the squared difference scores $D^2$\n```{=html}\n<style type=\"text/css\">\n</style>\n<table id=\"T_da31e\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th id=\"T_da31e_level0_col0\" class=\"col_heading level0 col0\" >ID</th>\n      <th id=\"T_da31e_level0_col1\" class=\"col_heading level0 col1\" >A</th>\n      <th id=\"T_da31e_level0_col2\" class=\"col_heading level0 col2\" >B</th>\n      <th id=\"T_da31e_level0_col3\" class=\"col_heading level0 col3\" >D</th>\n      <th id=\"T_da31e_level0_col4\" class=\"col_heading level0 col4\" >D^2</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row0_col0\" class=\"data row0 col0\" >1</td>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row0_col1\" class=\"data row0 col1\" >22</td>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row0_col2\" class=\"data row0 col2\" >24</td>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row0_col3\" class=\"data row0 col3\" >2</td>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row0_col4\" class=\"data row0 col4\" >4</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row1_col0\" class=\"data row1 col0\" >2</td>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row1_col1\" class=\"data row1 col1\" >22</td>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row1_col2\" class=\"data row1 col2\" >25</td>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row1_col3\" class=\"data row1 col3\" >3</td>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row1_col4\" class=\"data row1 col4\" >9</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row2_col0\" class=\"data row2 col0\" >3</td>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row2_col1\" class=\"data row2 col1\" >26</td>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row2_col2\" class=\"data row2 col2\" >25</td>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row2_col3\" class=\"data row2 col3\" >-1</td>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row2_col4\" class=\"data row2 col4\" >1</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row3_col0\" class=\"data row3 col0\" >4</td>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row3_col1\" class=\"data row3 col1\" >25</td>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row3_col2\" class=\"data row3 col2\" >26</td>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row3_col3\" class=\"data row3 col3\" >1</td>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row3_col4\" class=\"data row3 col4\" >1</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row4_col0\" class=\"data row4 col0\" >5</td>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row4_col1\" class=\"data row4 col1\" >23</td>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row4_col2\" class=\"data row4 col2\" >25</td>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row4_col3\" class=\"data row4 col3\" >2</td>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row4_col4\" class=\"data row4 col4\" >4</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row5_col0\" class=\"data row5 col0\" >6</td>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row5_col1\" class=\"data row5 col1\" >23</td>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row5_col2\" class=\"data row5 col2\" >25</td>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row5_col3\" class=\"data row5 col3\" >2</td>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row5_col4\" class=\"data row5 col4\" >4</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row6_col0\" class=\"data row6 col0\" >7</td>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row6_col1\" class=\"data row6 col1\" >26</td>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row6_col2\" class=\"data row6 col2\" >25</td>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row6_col3\" class=\"data row6 col3\" >-1</td>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row6_col4\" class=\"data row6 col4\" >1</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row7_col0\" class=\"data row7 col0\" >8</td>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row7_col1\" class=\"data row7 col1\" >23</td>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row7_col2\" class=\"data row7 col2\" >27</td>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row7_col3\" class=\"data row7 col3\" >4</td>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row7_col4\" class=\"data row7 col4\" >16</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row8_col0\" class=\"data row8 col0\" >9</td>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row8_col1\" class=\"data row8 col1\" >24</td>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row8_col2\" class=\"data row8 col2\" >29</td>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row8_col3\" class=\"data row8 col3\" >5</td>\n      <td id=\"T_da31e_row8_col4\" class=\"data row8 col4\" >25</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n```\n<br>New Summary statistics for the difference scores:<br>\n                             $$M_D = {1.89}, \\quad \\Sigma{D} = {17}, \\quad \\Sigma{D^2} = {65}$$ <br>\n                             \n<br>Calculate *SS* of the difference scores <br>\n                             $$SS_D = \\Sigma D^2 - \\frac{(\\Sigma D)^2}{n}$$ <br>\n                             $$SS_D = {65} - \\frac{289}{9}$$ <br>\n                             $$SS_D = {65} - {32.11}$$ <br>\n                             $$SS_D = {32.89}$$ <br><br>\n                             \nCalculate the variance of the difference scores <br>\n                             $$s_D^2 = \\frac{SS_D}{df}$$ <br>\n                             $$s_D^2 = \\frac{32.89}{8}$$ <br>\n                             $$s_D^2 = {4.11}$$ <br><br>\n                            \nCalculate the estimated standard error of the difference scores <br>\n                             $$s_{M_D} = \\sqrt{\\frac{s^2}{n}}$$ <br>\n                             $$s_{M_D} = \\sqrt{\\frac{4.11}{9}}$$ <br>\n                             $$s_{M_D} = \\sqrt{0.46}$$ <br>\n                             $$s_{M_D} = {0.68}$$ <br><br>\n                            \nCalculate $t_{obt}$ <br>\n                             $$t_{obt} = {\\frac{M_D - \\mu_D}{s_{M_D}}}$$ <br>\n                             $$t_{obt} = \\frac{1.89 - 0}{0.68}$$ <br>\n                             $$t_{obt} = \\frac{1.89}{0.68}$$ <br>\n                             $$t_{obt} = {2.78}$$ <br><br>\n                            \nCalculating Cohen's *d* <br>\n                             $$d = \\frac{M_D}{\\sqrt{s^2}}$$ <br>\n                             $$d = \\frac{1.89}{{{\\sqrt{4.11}}}}$$ <br>\n                             $$d = \\frac{1.89}{2.03}$$ <br>\n                             $$d = {0.93}$$ <br><br>\n                            \nThe results: <br><br>\nfail to reject the null hypothesis, results not significant, <br> *t*(8) = 2.78, *p* > 0.05, *d* = 0.93<br><br>\n\n\n",
